# Default Team Structure & Communication Setup

## Standard Team Structure (5 người)

| Role | Responsibility | Experience Level |
|------|----------------|------------------|
| Project Manager | Quản lý dự án, timeline, stakeholder communication | 3+ years blockchain projects |
| Lead Web3 Fullstack Developer | Architecture, smart contracts, frontend integration | 5+ years Web3 + Next.js |
| Senior Web3 Fullstack Developer | Backend, bridge protocols, oracle integration | 4+ years blockchain development |
| QA Engineer | Testing, automation, smart contract testing | 3+ years blockchain testing |
| UI/UX Designer | Interface design, UX optimization, bot design | 4+ years crypto applications |

## Standard Communication Channels

### Chat & Quick Updates
- **Primary:** Telegram group
- **Purpose:** Daily updates, technical discussions, quick questions
- **Format:** Text-based standups, no formal meetings required

### Official Documentation
- **Channel:** Email
- **Purpose:** Milestones, deliverables, formal approvals, change requests
- **Format:** Structured emails with clear action items

### Meetings & Reports
- **Platform:** Google Meet
- **Schedule:**
  - Weekly progress: Fridays, 30 minutes
  - Demo sessions: End of each sprint, 1 hour
  - Ad-hoc technical: As needed
- **Recording:** Optional based on project needs

